snippet.title: GUANTANAMERO | Are His Memories Real or Just Nightmares? | Full Movie
snippet.description:
A man washes ashore with no clear memory of how he arrived there.
The past keeps pulling him back, whether it’s real or not.

After a powerful storm, Ali wakes up alone on a deserted beach, confused and unwell. With nowhere else to turn, he is helped by locals who offer him temporary shelter in Havana. As Ali tries to recover, unsettling dreams and vivid visions begin to blur the line between memory and imagination, forcing him to question what truly happened to him — and whether he can ever leave the past behind.

Director: Vicente Peñarrocha
Cast: Mohamed Chafik, Ako Chavarri.
